Names of the settings stored in ospsuiteEnv. Can be used with getOSPSuiteUtilsSetting()

Source: R/ospsuite.utils-env.R
ospsuiteUtilsSettingNames.Rd

Names of the settings stored in ospsuiteEnv. Can be used with getOSPSuiteUtilsSetting()

Usage

ospsuiteUtilsSettingNames

Format

An object of class list of length 4.

Examples

ospsuiteUtilsSettingNames
#> $packageName
#> [1] "packageName"
#> 
#> $suiteName
#> [1] "suiteName"
#> 
#> $formatNumericsDigits
#> [1] "formatNumericsDigits"
#> 
#> $LOG_SAFE_EPSILON
#> [1] "LOG_SAFE_EPSILON"
#>
